2023-11-01 22:27:12.581 EDT [ 6543018c.20227 3/5501 ] postgres@tpcds1 LOG:  statement: COMMIT
2023-11-01 22:27:12.581 EDT [ 6543018c.20227 3/0 ] postgres@tpcds1 LOG:  duration: 0.073 ms
