2023-11-01 23:54:58.519 EDT [ 65431bc7.20615 3/5599 ] postgres@tpcds1 LOG:  statement: COMMIT
2023-11-01 23:54:58.519 EDT [ 65431bc7.20615 3/0 ] postgres@tpcds1 LOG:  duration: 0.057 ms
