2023-11-02 00:08:27.457 EDT [ 65431ef0.2073a 3/5697 ] postgres@tpcds1 LOG:  duration: 1987.941 ms
2023-11-02 00:08:27.457 EDT [ 65431ef0.2073a 3/5697 ] postgres@tpcds1 LOG:  statement: COMMIT
2023-11-02 00:08:27.457 EDT [ 65431ef0.2073a 3/0 ] postgres@tpcds1 LOG:  duration: 0.058 ms
