2023-11-02 00:13:14.713 EDT [ 65431ef0.2073a 3/5748 ] postgres@tpcds1 LOG:  statement: COMMIT
2023-11-02 00:13:14.713 EDT [ 65431ef0.2073a 3/0 ] postgres@tpcds1 LOG:  duration: 0.056 ms
